Experience in contracts and contract negotiations, and contract strategy development and execution 
Experience working and demonstrated experience influencing stakeholders and business partners 
Demonstrated experience in improving supply chain and supplier performance, including the use of cost models and objective based performance measures 
Experience working with Asia based suppliers 
Experience and knowledge with hardware design 
Knowledge of EMS/ODM/JDM/OEM business models, consignment & turnkey materials management, cost modeling, supply chain design, and reverse logistics 
Demonstrated experience driving a plan to bring resolution to differing opinions, reaching out across functional boundaries to drive collaboration and sharing credit in a team environment 
